  "san-jose": "San Jose, at the heart of Silicon Valley, has one of the most mature EV charging ecosystems in the country, shaped by decades of tech industry adoption and California's clean vehicle programs. Charging stations are densely distributed across the city, with strong coverage near tech campuses, Santana Row, the convention center, and major transit hubs. Workplace charging is particularly prevalent given the concentration of technology employers.",

