  "long-beach": "Long Beach combines its role as a major US port city with a growing commitment to sustainable transportation, including EV infrastructure. Charging stations are available near the Aquarium of the Pacific, the convention center, and throughout the city's retail corridors. The city's flat terrain and mild climate make it well-suited for EV driving, and the local port authority has invested in electric vehicle infrastructure as part of broader emissions reduction efforts.",

